jacdac.HeartRateReg.HeartRate:
Read-only bpm u16.16 (uint32_t). The estimated heart rate.
* ```
const [heartRate] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u16.16")
```
jacdac.HeartRateReg.HeartRateError:
Read-only bpm u16.16 (uint32_t). The estimated error on the reported sensor data.
* ```
const [heartRateError] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u16.16")
```
jacdac.HeartRateReg.Variant:
Constant Variant (uint8_t). The type of physical sensor
* ```
const [variant] = jdunpack<[jacdac.HeartRateVariant]>(buf, "u8")
```
modules.HeartRateClient:
A sensor approximating the heart rate.
*
**Jacdac is NOT suitable for medical devices and should NOT be used in any kind of device to diagnose or treat any medical conditions.**
modules.HeartRateClient.heartRateError: The estimated error on the reported sensor data.
modules.HeartRateClient.onHeartRateChang: Run code when the heart rate changes by the given threshold value.
